      <title>欧盟破碎的市场使财富陷入危险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-07/eu-s-broken-markets-put-wealth-in-peril-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[包括初创公司在内的欧洲公司正在努力获得适当的资金来增长，许多人选择在美国上市，那里的股票以比欧洲的60％溢价进行交易。彭博的Jan-Patrick Barnert打破了局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-07/eu-s-broken-markets-put-wealth-in-peril-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Feb 2025 07:21:57 GMT</pubDate>
